title: Ep. 68: 'Halt and Catch Fire' and 'Animal Kingdom' Re-up
description:
Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald discuss the Elliot-free episode of 'Mr. Robot' (8:00) and the return of AMC's 'Halt and Catch Fire' (15:30), then they give their thoughts on this summer's 'Animal Kingdom' and the rebranding of Turner networks (29:00).
